x 4 cm), no white pith and juiced","1 pinch raw sugar (optional)","1 pinch salt flakes","20 sprigs fresh coriander, leaves only"]},{"title":"Corn","content":["700 g water","3 corn cobs, silks and husks removed and cobs cut into halves","100 g Pecorino cheese, grated, to serve"]}],"id":"r115280","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-HRXMnqQMK2M\/XZWZ5keAW6I\/AAAAAAAAeTI\/e5EuTMsILe0KIdQ-bK0-jmnlU3bHDsddACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_oCXaW6lhfsCnFcUm.png","title":"Steamed corn with chipotle mayonnaise and coriander salsa","publishedAt":"2017-01-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"9.6 g","fat":"42.7 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"12.5 g","calories":"2000 kJ \/ 476 kcal"},"usefulItems":"jug, sealable container, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Chipotle in adobo are smoked jalapeño chillies in a tomato, garlic and oregano sauce. They are sold in tins in some supermarkets and specialty food stores. If you cannot find them, replace chillies with 2 teaspoons smoked paprika."],"basicInfo":["easy","35m","45m","6 portions"]}